Class Name

  • java.lang.Object
    • Name
  • public class Name
extends java.lang.Object
    Name class that can get and set a first name, middle initial, and last name, as well as get the normal order of the name, get the reverse order of the name, get the unity ID, get the initials of the name, get the length of the name, get the String version of the name, and check whether two names were equal or not.
    Author:
    Selena Chen, Ayushi Verma
